gnome-chromecast-player (2.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add internationalization support (i18n) with English and German translations
  * Improve README documentation with installation instructions
  * Bug fixes and stability improvements

 -- DaHool <torsten.mobi@gmail.com>  Tue, 16 Dec 2025 16:51:14 +0100

gnome-chromecast-player (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major version 2.0 release
  * Modern GTK4/Libadwaita interface
  * Hardware acceleration support (AMD, NVIDIA, Intel)
  * Chromecast streaming with device discovery
  * YouTube video playback via URL
  * Playlist management with thumbnails
  * Subtitle support (SRT, ASS, VTT)
  * Multiple audio track selection
  * Video effects and filters (rotation, zoom, crop, gamma, filters)
  * A-B loop functionality for learning
  * Chapter navigation support
  * Frame-by-frame navigation
  * Playback speed control (0.25x to 3.0x)
  * Screenshot capture
  * Video equalizer (brightness, contrast, saturation, hue)
  * Timeline thumbnails
  * Keyboard shortcuts with help dialog
  * Playlist import (M3U, PLS)
  * Multi-room audio with Chromecast groups

 -- DaHool <torsten.mobi@gmail.com>  Sun, 15 Dec 2025 12:00:00 +0100
